# AUDIO::TRIGGER_MUSIC_EVENT

## Summary
Triggers the specified music event (any associated actions as set up in RAVE)

## Parameters
* **STRING** eventName

## Returns
* **BOOL**: TRUE if the event was triggered, FALSE otherwise
